last_episode_to_air.overview: Youssef El Sherif plays the role of a young lawyer named "Ali", who comes to him with a call "unknown number", then he replies to it, and he talks to him with many problems, and he is exposed to a violent hurricane within a few days , especially his strict principles, and his ideas of honor and honesty. You will commit crimes that could not have occured , so what if he is the one who commits it? Can a phone call change the course of your life so that you wish you didn't answer it?
